snippet: Washington State’s star receiver, Marquess Wilson, was suspended on Monday for an unspecified violation of team rules, and will miss Saturday’s game against No. 17 UCLA.
lead_paragraph: Washington State’s star receiver, Marquess Wilson, was suspended on Monday for an unspecified violation of team rules, and will miss Saturday’s game against No. 17 UCLA.

headline.seo: Washington State Suspends Receiver Marquess Wilson
headline.main: Washington State Suspends Star Wide Receiver
